  Paper Dungeons is a 2D Puzzle RPG, boosted by online content. With the
  ability to create and share online your own levels, you are up for an
  infinite replay value. The game is visualized as a classic tabletop board
  game structured like a dungeon crawling game with a puzzle component. You
  can destroy walls and auto-heal as you uncover new dungeon tiles, with 3
  different and originals gameplays: ADVENTURE, PUZZLE and ROGUE. Even if the
  game presents some online features, you can still play offline.
